            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Quintus Fabius Isio, son of Quintus, (set this up) for Laelia Coprilla his wife, freedwoman of Decimus</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The style of plaque, a thick heavy square block of this sort is quite typical for Thermae Himeraeae.</p>
